	(
		148,
		'\'COLDSHIELD\'',
		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: c \'coldshield\'\r\n\r\nA reasonably experienced sorcerer of the cold has the ability to create a shield\r\nof freezing air around them, both protecting the sorcerer from bashing and\r\ncausing harm to their would-be basher.',
