	(
		149,
		'\'FRIGID AURA\'',
		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: c \'frigid aura\'\r\n\r\nIn order to make their foes a bit less comfortable with the thought of combating\r\nthem, cold sorcerers have developed a way to cause harm to anyone who comes\r\nclose enough to attack them. This is accomplished by the removal of heat from\r\nthe area around the sorcerer, so that whoever enters this area is chilled.',
