		'DETECT HIDDEN',
		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: detect\r\n\r\nThis skill allows the user to heighten his or her perception such as to be\r\nable to detect those who are hiding.\r\n\r\nAlso see: THIEF HIDE',
		''
	),
	(
