		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: slash <object> <target>\r\n\r\nUsing a sharp weapon, the thief can attempt to spill the contents of a\r\nsack someone else is holding by slashing at it, in hopes of cutting it \r\nopen.\r\n\r\nAlso see: THIEF',
