		'Gawinn'
	),
	(
		547,
		'\'LORE\'',
		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: lore (object)\r\n\r\nThe art of item lore draws upon myths, legends, and common sense to gain \r\ninformation on an item. The better ones skill becomes, the easier they \r\nwill be able to make sense of the item in question.',
		'Gawinn'
