	(
		548,
		'\'RAGE\'',
		'horde',
		0,
		'Syntax: call \'rage\'\r\n\r\nThe ability to call the great spirit of an animal to fill you with rage is \r\nmighty indeed. While in this rage you will lunge at nearly anything in \r\nyour path. Each spirit will infuse you with it\'s own strengths, \r\nweaknesses, and abilities while you are enraged. The rage is so strong at \r\ntimes it is possible even other members of the Horde are not safe. ',
		'Gawinn'
