	(
		550,
		'FLEE',
		'none',
		0,
		'Syntax: flee\r\n\r\nEven the simplest of simpletons has an innate knowledge of how to run away. \r\nCertain classes may gain skills to impede the effectiveness of their \r\nopponent fleeing while other classes may learn to counter those measures or \r\nbecome more efficient in the mighty art of running away.\r\n',
		'Ustephiel'
	),
	(
		551,
